title: 39 more people die with Covid-19, 493 additional cases
description: The Department of Health has confirmed that 39 more people have died from Covid-19, bringing the overall death toll here to 610.
content:
The Department of Health has confirmed that 39 more people have died with Covid-19, bringing the overall death toll here to 610.
A further 445 new cases of coronavirus have been diagnosed. In addition, there are 48 cases of Covid-19 from the backlog of tests… [+2359 chars]
